<font color="#FF0000">HOLD YOUR FIRE!</font><br>
<tt>Fri Nov 14 23:34:41 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I am not made to feel inferior when I am attacked by strange people.  My greatest pain occurs when so called normal masses ignore or reject my needs, especially the U.S. Government.<br><br>
Antagonists don't threaten me but they do excite a counter attack mechanism in the back of my mind.  I don't have to get sloppy drunk in order to deal with a drunk.. I don't have to get irrational and stupid to deal with sick people.<br>
No need to argue with a stump or get into an altercation with someone who is mentally ill... ends up being a lose-lose situation.  I don't care to lose any more of what I have...and they have nothing to lose.<br><br>
Probably, won't amount to much.  Marc will handle the situation.. which frees us up to continue.  Hope we don't have to wait until Monday.. but no big deal.<br><br>
Watch where you step!  Keep the pledge!<br><br>
Mustang Two Four
